subject: Golf
lead_paragraph: Helen Alfredsson shot a course-record nine-under-par 63 to pull one shot behind the leader, Angela Park, after the second round of the Evian Masters in Evian-les-Bains, France. Park shot a 68 for a 10-under 134 total. Lorena Ochoa (73) is at six under.
